    "(3) The simulators for E/E architectures are reviewed comprehensively, including both network layer and vehicle functions layer.The rest of this paper is organized as follows.",
    "Section 2 reviews the development of E/E architecture topologies.",
    "Section 3 presents the application of networking technologies in E/E architectures comprehensively.",
    "Section 4 introduces the simulation verification method of the automotive E/E architectures.",
    "In Sect. 5, some challenges and open questions are discussed."
